text: VIK Televizija or Vlasenički informativni kanal was a local Bosnian public cable television channel based in Vlasenica municipality. It was founded in 2005 and it was closed in 2013. == References == == External links == * Website of CRA BiH * Official website of Vlasenica municipality Category:2005 establishments in Bosnia and Herzegovina Category:Television channels and stations established in 2005 Category:Television stations in Bosnia and Herzegovina Category:Television channels and stations disestablished in 2013
